<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Withdrawal Rejection Email</title>
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #f0f0f0; /* Light Gray */
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        background-color: #2f4f4f; /* Dark Gray */
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .header h2 {
        color: #f0f7f4; /* Light Green */
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }
      .content {
        color: #f0f7f4; /* Light Gray */
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
      .content strong {
        color: #125699; /* Light Green */
      }
      .content p {
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
      .consu {
        background: #f0f7f4;
        color: #125699; /* Dark Navy Blue */
        padding: 12px 16px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .button-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        margin: 10px 5px;
        border: 1px solid transparent;
        border-radius: 5px;
        cursor: pointer;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #ffffff; /* White */
      }
      .btn-primary {
        background-color: #4682b4; /* Steel Blue */
      }
      .btn-secondary {
        background-color: #1e90ff; /* Dodger Blue */
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #f0f7f4;
      }
      .footer a {
        color: #1e90ff; /* Light Green */
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h2>WealthBuilders</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h3>Hello, <span class="color-danger">{{name}}</span></h3>
        <p>
          Unfortunately, your withdrawal request for <strong>${{amount}}</strong> has been rejected. We apologize for any inconvenience this may have caused.
        </p>
        <p>
          Withdrawal Details:
          <br />
          <strong>Wallet Address:</strong> {{walletAddress}}
        </p>
        <p class="consu">
          For further assistance or inquiries, please feel free to contact our support team.
        </p>
        <div class="button-container">
          <a href="https://www.wealthbuilders.com/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Support</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Thank you for choosing WealthBuilders.</p>
        <p>
          Visit our website: 
          <a href="https://www.wealthbuilders.com">www.wealthbuilders.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
